        "explanation": "Explanation:\nThe divisors of 919191 are 1,7,13,911, 7, 13, 911,7,13,91, out of which only 111 and 777 are in the range [1,10][1, 10][1,10]. Therefore, the answer is max⁡(1,7)=7\\max(1, 7) = 7max(1,7)=7."
